# sira public dns rollout readiness — 20260425

status: readiness-manifested
created_at: 2026-04-25 23:19:30
repo_root: /Users/thien/Desktop/Hồ Sơ SHTT/ natt-os_verANC

---

## 1. principle

dns public chỉ được mở sau khi route gate, host guard, dns smoke, hardening matrix và sirasign frame guard đều pass.

public dns không được bypass natt domain gateway.

public dns không được expose admin route, secret route, audit write route hoặc internal route.

public dns không được dùng wildcard mở rộng khi chưa có deny-by-default.

---

## 2. allowed public surface

```text
apps.sira      -> public app entry, allow only safe read/app routes
mach.sira      -> mạch heyna transport entry, allow only /mach/heyna and approved transport routes
render.sira    -> render pilot/read surface, deny seal/write route
tam.sira       -> tenant fixture app surface, protected by gateway
audit.sira     -> audit read surface only, deny direct write
core.sira      -> core health/readiness only, deny admin
```

---

## 3. deny surface

```text
localhost public access -> deny
127.0.0.1 public access -> deny
unknown.sira -> deny
mail.sira -> deny
smtp.sira -> deny
imap.sira -> deny
/admin -> deny
/api/secret -> deny
/identity -> deny unless explicitly framed
/audit/write-direct -> deny
/render/seal -> deny
/finance/secret -> deny
```

---

## 4. dns provider action outside repo

```text
step 1: point public records to gateway only
step 2: tls certificate on gateway layer
step 3: gateway validates host before route
step 4: route gate validates path
step 5: sirasign frame guard validates sensitive frame
step 6: dns smoke runner verifies allow/deny matrix
```

---

## 5. required local gates before public switch

```text
tools/validate_sira_dns_zone_manifest.sira
tools/validate_sira_gateway_route_binding.sira
tools/validate_sira_gateway_hardening.sira
tools/run_sira_dns_smoke_matrix.sira
tools/validate_sira_dns_smoke_runner.sira
tools/run_sira_gateway_hardening_matrix.sira
tools/validate_sira_gateway_hardening_matrix.sira
tools/validate_sirasign_frame_guard.sira
tools/run_sirasign_frame_guard_matrix.sira
tools/validate_sirasign_frame_guard_matrix.sira
tools/validate_lowercase_surface.sira
tools/thiên gate
```

---

## 6. go / no-go rule

```text
go only if all local gates pass
no-go if any transport_error, timeout, wildcard exposure, admin allow, secret allow, direct audit write allow, or frame bypass appears
```
